<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Performance Materials Lab | UNC Charlotte</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0b1929;
    --navy-mid: #142036;
    --navy-light: #1e3050;
    --gold: #c8963e;
    --gold-light: #e8b86d;
    --cream: #f4efe6;
    --cream-dim: #ddd5c3;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: rgba(244,239,230,0.55);
    --border: rgba(200,150,62,0.2);
    --section-pad: 96px 0;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ===== NAV ===== */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 0 48px;
    height: 68px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(11,25,41,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
  }
  .nav-logo .lab-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .nav-logo .institution {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(200,150,62,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,150,62,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-bg-orb {
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px;
    right: -160px;
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(20,48,80,0.9) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 88px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    padding-bottom: 48px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stat-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(200,150,62,0.1); }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    left: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--text-muted);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; width: 40px; }
    50% { opacity: 1; width: 60px; }
  }

  /* ===== SECTION UTILITY ===== */
  section { padding: var(--section-pad); }
  .container { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px; }

  .section-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-label::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== RESEARCH ===== */
  .research-section { background: var(--navy-mid); }

  .research-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .research-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .research-card {
    background: var(--navy-light);
    padding: 40px 36px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    border-top: 2px solid transparent;
  }
  .research-card:hover { background: rgba(30,48,80,0.95); border-top-color: var(--gold); }

  .card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }
  .card-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; fill: none; stroke: currentColor; stroke-width: 1.5; }

  .card-number {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(200,150,62,0.08);
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .research-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .research-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .card-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(200,150,62,0.4);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .card-link {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .card-link::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transition: width 0.2s;
  }
  .research-card:hover .card-link::after { width: 40px; }

  /* ===== ABOUT ===== */
  .about-section { background: var(--navy); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }
  .about-image-frame {
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 110%;
    background: var(--navy-light);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-image-frame img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(30%);
  }
  .about-image-placeholder {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--navy-mid);
  }
  .about-image-placeholder svg { width: 40px; height: 40px; stroke: var(--gold); fill: none; opacity: 0.5; }

  .about-accent-bar {
    position: absolute;
    left: -16px;
    bottom: 32px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 80px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .about-text {}
  .about-text h2 { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-text p strong {
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-credentials {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .credential {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }
  .credential-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .credential-org {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ===== NEWS ===== */
  .news-section { background: var(--navy-mid); }

  .news-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }

  .news-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .news-card {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .news-card:hover { background: rgba(11,25,41,0.85); }

  .news-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    background: var(--navy-light);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .news-image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--navy-light);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .news-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .news-dot { width: 3px; height: 3px; background: var(--gold); border-radius: 50%; }

  .news-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .news-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .news-link {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .news-link::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 20px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transition: width 0.2s;
  }
  .news-card:hover .news-link::after { width: 36px; }

  /* ===== AFFILIATIONS ===== */
  .affiliations {
    background: var(--navy-light);
    padding: 48px 0;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }
  .affiliations-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 64px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .affil-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .affil-item:hover { opacity: 1; }
  .affil-name {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
  }
  .affil-role {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .affil-badge {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,150,62,0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
  footer {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 64px 0 40px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .footer-brand {}
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .footer-inst {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .footer-brand p {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .footer-col h5 {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
  .footer-col li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .footer-col a {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--cream); }

  .footer-bottom {
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .footer-bottom p {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ===== ANIMATION ===== */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-eyebrow  { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s both ease-out; }
  .hero h1       { animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.25s both ease-out; }
  .hero-sub      { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s both ease-out; }
  .hero-stats    { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.55s both ease-out; }
  .hero-actions  { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.7s both ease-out; }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== NAV ===== -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <span class="lab-name">Performance Materials Lab</span>
    <span class="institution">University of North Carolina at Charlotte</span>
  </div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#research">Research</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Teaching</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Publications</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">News</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Gallery</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Dr. Tipton</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-bg-orb"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Performance Materials Lab &nbsp;|&nbsp; EPIC Hall 3186</div>
    <h1>Where <em>Materials</em><br>Meet Mission</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Advancing clean water, next-generation coatings, and sustainable materials science from the Arctic to the Caribbean. Powered by 25 years of industry know-how and rigorous fundamental science.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">3</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Active NSF Programs</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">2</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Pending Patent Applications</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">R/V</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Dawn Research Vessel</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">25+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years in Industry</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#research" class="btn-primary">Explore Research</a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost">Meet Dr. Tipton</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span class="scroll-line"></span>
    Scroll to explore
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== RESEARCH ===== -->
<section class="research-section" id="research">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="research-header">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">Research Programs</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Three Pillars of<br>Scientific Inquiry</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-intro">The PML operates at the intersection of materials science, environmental chemistry, and engineering. Our programs combine bench-level discovery with real-world field campaigns.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="research-grid">

      <div class="research-card">
        <span class="card-number">01</span>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Advanced Materials &amp; BAM Ceramics</h3>
        <p>Developing AlMgB14 (BAM) ceramic coatings as a PFAS-free replacement for Teflon in cookware and industrial applications. First-ever optical characterization of BAM reveals semiconducting behavior that contradicts prior theory.</p>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">NSF DMR/CER</span>
          <span class="tag">Patent Pending</span>
          <span class="tag">PFAS-Free</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="card-link">View research</a>
      </div>

      <div class="research-card">
        <span class="card-number">02</span>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>PFAS &amp; Ocean Contamination</h3>
        <p>Tracking PFAS transport from Arctic to Caribbean waters aboard R/V Dawn. NSF EAGER Award #2444939 supports a global baseline dataset spanning the geographic North Pole, magnetic North Pole, and the Indian River Lagoon.</p>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">NSF EAGER</span>
          <span class="tag">Ocean Science</span>
          <span class="tag">R/V Dawn</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="card-link">View research</a>
      </div>

      <div class="research-card">
        <span class="card-number">03</span>
        <div class="card-icon">
